Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.22,0:22:47.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(83,125)}欢迎来到virgin road
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:51.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(125,83)}我也能和爸爸一起走吗？
