Comment: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,=========正文============
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓果然不同凡响啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮  羡慕死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说要当结婚杂志的模特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为我也能穿轻飘飘的可爱衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.08,0:00:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  对方要求有一个男性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.75,0:00:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们的事务所又没人选
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  我要闹别扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:41.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很适合真君呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.91,0:00:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且这条领带的品味也让人佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到第一次穿婚纱是工作需要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前觉得自己在此之前就已经结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚欲望很强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但总觉得像这样努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.52,0:02:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天能遇到我的白马王子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  制作人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件礼服马上就要换掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  午休后就要换别的衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.33,0:03:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是发给朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(60,20)\fs18}「我要奔向幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(135,40)\fs18}真抱歉  其实我下个月28号就要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(83,60)\fs18}虽然说好不会偷跑的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(50,80)\fs18}真的很抱歉」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样…发送
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.06,0:03:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友美一定会吓一跳的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  友美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用这么惊讶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算结婚又有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.49,0:03:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你的骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.82,0:03:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实只是结婚杂志的模特而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次见面再好好聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该马上就能请到假了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.92,0:03:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…我什么时候走到这里来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.80,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快让开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  您掉东西…了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.69,0:04:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  找到新娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  回婚礼现场了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…还有摄影…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓小姐到哪里去打电话了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便当都已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.63,0:04:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是梓小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.22,0:04:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓…梓小姐被拐走了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  我亲眼看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是梓的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作人  现在立刻就去救人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美希  我们会尽快回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我们拖延下时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美希我会试试的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:08.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明白您不愿意和从未相识的人结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们的主人是很了不起的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也一定会满意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之立刻回到婚礼现场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.17,0:05:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…请问是不是认错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是三浦梓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要穿那么容易混淆的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了  是结婚戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得还给那位新娘才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  工作室那边也要回去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:06:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  我到底是从哪里过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不干  这种父母间决定的婚事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打死都不干
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.77,0:06:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样说  我们主人也是打心底想要娶您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都把先祖代代相传的传家宝戒送您了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是其证明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种戒指还你就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.75,0:06:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来…刚才那人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的  是传家宝戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快回去找
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机也掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎么去工作室…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  坐出租车就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  我想问一下路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.99,0:07:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我离开村庄来这里见儿子但却迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去那个叫Land  Land  Tower的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那地方好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就在那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真对不起  我也在赶路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮忙了  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.40,0:07:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是先带您去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作人  再快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别强人所难了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.66,0:07:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那辆车…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作人  就是那辆车拐走梓小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出租车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请跟着前面那辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是警察什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  是艺人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  把梓小姐带哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓？是刚才那人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人也在找戒指吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急联络
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在车站目击到穿着婚纱的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员立即前往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解  赶快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让戒指被抢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.83,0:08:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  诱拐犯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真  很危险的  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请给我发票
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标从车站前往中华街
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全员立即前往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.30,0:08:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我也一起找
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我带路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别废话  带我去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉  我忘记自己也是路盲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  我一个人肯定也会迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  俊嗣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  没迷路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说在那个Land  Land  Tower碰面的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是约好在这个Marine  Port  Tower等吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是您带母亲过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道该怎么办了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里哪里  只是路盲碰巧走对路而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了  再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆也保重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我也要快点找辆出租车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:09:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个孩子的母亲在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.59,0:10:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解  发现后立即确保
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有消息说在肉包子店目击到那女的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是刚才那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会把梓小姐交给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很烫要当心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.63,0:10:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好  我也想让她吹吹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去买肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs22}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:52.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开  让开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那个…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.89,0:11:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓小姐～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像听到了真的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.61,0:11:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来这是幸运肉包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金钱运一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱运马马虎虎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要找的人在前方3米？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.47,0:11:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  我也该回去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是呢  三浦小姐和菊地君都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就只剩你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.53,0:11:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正待会儿也要拍她的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.40,0:11:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在三浦回来之前先拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.53,0:11:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只有这样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:11:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快点准备一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用着急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在梓她们回来之前  要给美希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什  你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认  认错人了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓  你在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.74,0:12:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.99,0:12:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不过刚才那人挺帅的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥都画不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:56.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么能激发灵感呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵感来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真头疼啊  哪都找不到出租车站  咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子疼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  能拜托你看下店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.57,0:14:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶快点回去工作才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.38,0:14:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  能帮我占卜一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好  那个  不过可能不准
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.24,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好精彩的电影啊  正好到高潮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个演员  好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实啊  我被跟我有婚约的女士甩掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今天就要离开日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以最后想在日本找一个能留下美好回忆的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该去哪比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.36,0:15:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这个  要怎么用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是塔罗牌还能懂一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  万事试为先
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是港口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  我就去看一看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.31,0:15:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人只有一个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,费用放在里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.98,0:16:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是帮大忙了  必须要好好答谢你才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.07,0:16:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来  能告诉我出租车站在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  就这事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个的话  看  在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美希个人觉得婚纱再加点跃动感会比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错啊  很新颖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  摄影师  美希突然想在海边拍摄了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人  真的往这里来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  有目击情报说走过这个天桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这前面有什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摩天轮和港口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是个难得的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然和出租车的队伍搞错  排到摩天轮的队伍去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  风景真是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.43,0:17:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  戒指在我这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能听到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.36,0:17:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  请快点让我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  是最高级的金华火腿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快停下来啊  店都乱套了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.59,0:17:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样根本做不了生意了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商品的损失  你要赔偿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  就算你这么对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  不好了  目标往港口去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  没工夫在这瞎耗了  快追快追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.07,0:18:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那边好像发生什么事了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.97,0:18:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在啊  去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  哎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓  我马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快把戒指夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快赔钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你对我这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种金额的支票  我受不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请一定接受肉包子的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画  请收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  戒指  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.35,0:19:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这附近和想像的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那么开始布置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.91,0:19:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.25,0:19:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  戒指  戒指…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  梓  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戒指在我这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丢失的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  呐  摄影师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  绝对要拍下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…来送戒指的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.08,0:20:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了它  你一定很为难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物归原主了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你们的主人在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种戒指  给我都不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是  太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.27,0:20:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石油王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  居然是这种超级帅哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面  我是石油王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的求婚  我接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.41,0:21:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来  你的占卜很准啊  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也要幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真  这演的是哪出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…我也一头雾水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真  制作人  来接我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  梓  平安就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.78,0:21:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的拍摄  还赶得上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以了  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的照片  已经拍下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:49.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  登载了登载了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.71,0:21:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.46,0:21:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个杂志  因为这张照片而大受好评哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断地增印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:22:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓和龙宫小町的知名度也是一下子提高了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.39,0:22:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也登载了很多美希和真的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  看啊  这个真非常帅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中华街的修理费  都是石油王出的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.19,0:22:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  因为一半是他们的原因啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,友美发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(70,20)\fs18}「告诉你一个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(40,40)\fs18}那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(110,60)\fs18}听说没有婚约却穿了婚纱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(63,80)\fs18}婚期会延迟哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:29.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说没有婚约却穿了婚纱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.46,0:22:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚期会延迟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾啊  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.34,0:22:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,==============================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.54,0:23:58.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周的偶像大师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是水濑伊织
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.26,0:24:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家全都是幸运儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.55,0:24:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为每周都能看到伊织的漂亮脸蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.39,0:24:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以下周也
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.60,0:24:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好期待吧
